                "content": "<p>其实平时刷知乎，经常看到一些抄袭的视频和图片，但文字内容抄袭并不多。</p><p>但今天下午刷知乎看到一个回答，发现了一个100%纯氪金抄袭用户。</p><a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/274095849/answer/372244703\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\"internal\">既然中美差距这么大，我们为什么非要和美国打贸易战不可呢？</a><p>作者是 <a class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/82dfa2c58fa53ca93a56d70d114aef16\" data-hash=\"82dfa2c58fa53ca93a56d70d114aef16\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$82dfa2c58fa53ca93a56d70d114aef16\">@厦可导</a> ，写的是贸易战开打后，网络上的一个流行段子。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><img src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-bafa47ed397d4759a7e0c94128fee2a2_b.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"678\" data-rawheight=\"541\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"678\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-bafa47ed397d4759a7e0c94128fee2a2_r.jpg\"/></figure><p>我的第一印象就觉得这不是作者，于是网上搜了下，作者就是知乎大神 <a class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/8a88eccbb3c3e498a80d7294e19348d0\" data-hash=\"8a88eccbb3c3e498a80d7294e19348d0\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$8a88eccbb3c3e498a80d7294e19348d0\">@宁南山</a> 。</p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/35894127\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-dd71c3a6af8f92e92b98d5d4b6d23274_180x120.jpg\" data-image-width=\"819\" data-image-height=\"460\" class=\"internal\">宁南山：勇敢者的游戏--由中兴开始的2018中美芯片战</a><p>而这个<a class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/82dfa2c58fa53ca93a56d70d114aef16\" data-hash=\"82dfa2c58fa53ca93a56d70d114aef16\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$82dfa2c58fa53ca93a56d70d114aef16\">@厦可导</a> 只是对原文进行了小范围加工，就直接作答，并收获了3.8K赞（截止4月23日下午5点）。于是我果断进行了举报。</p><p>要知道，普通用户认真回答多久，才能获得这么多赞啊。这位厦门大学的同学随便复制，粗略修改下就能疯狂吸赞了——果不其然，这问题评论下还有不明情况的吃瓜群众跪舔他。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-2ad57b1f4d85a395788b381d9f761ef3_b.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"661\" data-rawheight=\"579\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"661\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-2ad57b1f4d85a395788b381d9f761ef3_r.jpg\"/></figure><p>问题来了。</p><p>之后，我又看到了 <a class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/82dfa2c58fa53ca93a56d70d114aef16\" data-hash=\"82dfa2c58fa53ca93a56d70d114aef16\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$82dfa2c58fa53ca93a56d70d114aef16\">@厦可导</a> 的其他回答。</p><a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/272262183/answer/366535344\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-302d4da51e942cafd5d86ccb0db98560_180x120.jpg\" data-image-width=\"465\" data-image-height=\"272\" class=\"internal\">如何看待美国联合英国法国空袭叙利亚？</a><figure data-size=\"normal\"><img src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-f41a6773e154b9fc356a3bd3d10564de_b.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"708\" data-rawheight=\"653\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"708\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-f41a6773e154b9fc356a3bd3d10564de_r.jpg\"/></figure><p>原文抄袭前知乎用户 <a class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/a07046db081571f2985283ba71ab15ec\" data-hash=\"a07046db081571f2985283ba71ab15ec\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$a07046db081571f2985283ba71ab15ec\">@明公</a> 的公众号文章。</p><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//mp.weixin.qq.com/s%3Fsrc%3D11%26timestamp%3D1524475811%26ver%3D834%26signature%3DDR4UnL8APFyavwCqdsiOOL1qKi7wvrhfkkwWt%2AyddZqYPFKYijth6TfuJO8UBbUJCZFBN6wDJ0vD76r-4FBkuubgPzlajysmOvW9pGANACSSnWz82GMMD%2Ar1fIck1Fcq%26new%3D1\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">美俄叙利亚剑拔弩张，中美贸易战初现曙光</a><p>看这位的信息来自厦门大学，今天心情不佳，我甚至有人肉这货的冲动。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><img src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-b5e464e554aa5e68ea1949221379914a_b.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1022\" data-rawheight=\"506\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1022\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-b5e464e554aa5e68ea1949221379914a_r.jpg\"/></figure><p>就这B样还想带人逛厦大呢？</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-a837697adc409660a09f70961a36a673_b.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"2000\" data-rawheight=\"625\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"2000\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-a837697adc409660a09f70961a36a673_r.jpg\"/></figure><p>真的， <a class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/82dfa2c58fa53ca93a56d70d114aef16\" data-hash=\"82dfa2c58fa53ca93a56d70d114aef16\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$82dfa2c58fa53ca93a56d70d114aef16\">@厦可导</a>这种用户，真的让人看得膈应。一瞬间会让人失去创作的欲望。</p><p>你不杀伯仁，伯仁却因你而死。对这种用户的每一次点赞，都是对知乎创造环境的破坏。</p><p>不怼不快。希望知乎严打这些用户，给我们一些基本的游戏体验。 <a class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/b6f80220378c8b0b78175dd6a0b9c680\" data-hash=\"b6f80220378c8b0b78175dd6a0b9c680\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$b6f80220378c8b0b78175dd6a0b9c680\">@黄继新</a> <a class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/6733f12c60e7e98ea7491f20de46f79e\" data-hash=\"6733f12c60e7e98ea7491f20de46f79e\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$6733f12c60e7e98ea7491f20de46f79e\">@周源</a> <a class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/401f6c00951ab2723222374df7cdeb96\" data-hash=\"401f6c00951ab2723222374df7cdeb96\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$401f6c00951ab2723222374df7cdeb96\">@武汉北</a> </p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><p>更新：知乎还是速度，文章发出半小时，已经将此人处理。666</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><img src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-678dbe7c6f82b5dee6283ca710571e96_b.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"704\" data-rawheight=\"157\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"704\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-678dbe7c6f82b5dee6283ca710571e96_r.jpg\"/></figure><p></p>",
